    <title>2024java教学实训</title>
    <url>/2024/05/22/2024java%E6%95%99%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%9E%E8%AE%AD/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>2024夏java教学实习</p>
<span id="more"></span>


<p>关于注解<br>依赖注入，对象注入IOC容器</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Mybatis</span><br><span class="line">@Mapper</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Spring</span><br><span class="line">@Component  总</span><br><span class="line">@Controller controller</span><br><span class="line">@Service    service</span><br><span class="line">@Repository dao</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">spring自动注入</span><br><span class="line">@Autowired</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<p>动态SQL</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;<span class="keyword">if</span>&gt;&lt;/if&gt;</span><br><span class="line">用于判断条件是否成立，如果条件为<span class="literal">true</span>，则拼接SQL</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="built_in">where</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">where</span>元素只会在子元素有内容的情况下才插入<span class="built_in">where</span>子句，而且会</span><br><span class="line">自动去除子句的开头的AND或OR</span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="built_in">set</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">动态地在行首插入 SET 关键字，并会删掉额外的逗号。（用在</span><br><span class="line">update语句中</span><br><span class="line">&lt;sql&gt;</span><br><span class="line">定义可重用的SQL片段,抽取相同部分,用<span class="built_in">id</span>作以标注</span><br><span class="line">&lt;insert&gt;</span><br><span class="line">通过属性refid，指定包含的SQL片段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>java</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>java</tag>
      </tags>
