  <entry>
    <title>关于git拉取项目中一些配置指令</title>
    <url>/2024/02/23/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Egit%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%96%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="报错信息"><a href="#报错信息" class="headerlink" title="报错信息"></a>报错信息</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">error: RPC failed; result=18, HTTP code = 200194.00 KiB/s    </span><br><span class="line">fatal: The remote end hung up unexpectedly</span><br><span class="line">fatal: 过早的文件结束符（EOF）</span><br><span class="line">fatal: index-pack failed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>

<p>在多次修改后存在两个问题 一是在于传输速度的限制 二是git内存的问题<br>修改git配置后解决</p>
<h3 id="初次修改"><a href="#初次修改" class="headerlink" title="初次修改"></a>初次修改</h3><p>对于提交缓存修改大小</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.postBuffer 524288000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>也可以设置更大的值</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.postBuffer 1048576000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注： 参数 –global 针对当前用户生效 ， 设置所有用户使用 –system</p>
<h2 id="二次修改"><a href="#二次修改" class="headerlink" title="二次修改"></a>二次修改</h2><p>对配置git的之地速度和最低时间</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.lowSpeedLimit 0</span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.lowSpeedTime 999999</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里的时间单位是秒</p>
<h2 id="三次修改"><a href="#三次修改" class="headerlink" title="三次修改"></a>三次修改</h2><p>问题在于git内存不够引起的报错</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global core.compression 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注：未求证部分<br>可以修改以下配置，得到相同的效果</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[core] </span><br><span class="line">packedGitLimit = 512m </span><br><span class="line">packedGitWindowSize = 512m </span><br><span class="line">[pack] </span><br><span class="line">deltaCacheSize = 2047m </span><br><span class="line">packSizeLimit = 2047m </span><br><span class="line">windowMemory = 2047m</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>git配置指令设置</p>
<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wcf2328/article/details/103211767">https://blog.csdn.net/wcf2328/article/details/103211767</a></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>git</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>git</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>关于hyperledger fabric通道占用问题</title>
    <url>/2024/01/20/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Ehyperledger-fabric%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%E5%8D%A0%E7%94%A8%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>环境为ubuntu20.04，hyperledger2.5</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<p>在linux系统下<br>首先修改resolv.conf内容</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/resolv.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注释其中的optins内容</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#optins</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后输入以下命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker stop $(docker ps -aq)</span><br><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">rm</span> -f $(docker ps -aq)</span><br><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">rm</span>  $(docker ps -a | grep <span class="string">&quot;hyperledger/*&quot;</span> | awk <span class="string">&quot;&#123;print \$1&#125;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">docker-compose down --volumes --remove-orphans</span><br><span class="line">docker volume prune</span><br><span class="line">docker network prune</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>重新启动项目即可</p>
<p>删除命令<br>rm -rf()</p>
<p>Vmware虚拟机磁盘扩充问题<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_52103018/article/details/120297379">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_52103018/article/details/120297379</a></p>
]]></content>
