        <category>区块链</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>hyperledger fabric</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>关于python实例的学习笔记</title>
    <url>/2024/03/22/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Epython%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>关于python学习的笔记</p>
<p>基本算法和函数和一些标准库的学习</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="1-判断各国是数字的字符"><a href="#1-判断各国是数字的字符" class="headerlink" title="1 判断各国是数字的字符"></a>1 判断各国是数字的字符</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import unicodedata</span><br><span class="line">unicodedata.numeric(<span class="string">&quot;字符&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-各个进制的转换"><a href="#2-各个进制的转换" class="headerlink" title="2 各个进制的转换"></a>2 各个进制的转换</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">十进制数为： dec</span><br><span class="line">二进制： bin(dec)</span><br><span class="line">八进制：oct(dec)</span><br><span class="line">十六进制：hex(dec)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-ASCII码与字符相互转换"><a href="#3-ASCII码与字符相互转换" class="headerlink" title="3 ASCII码与字符相互转换"></a>3 ASCII码与字符相互转换</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">转为ASCII：ord(<span class="string">&quot;字符&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">转为字符：chr(数字)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="4-日历库"><a href="#4-日历库" class="headerlink" title="4 日历库"></a>4 日历库</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import calendar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="5-字符串判断"><a href="#5-字符串判断" class="headerlink" title="5 字符串判断"></a>5 字符串判断</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.isalnum()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是数字或者字母</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.isalpha()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是字母</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.isdigit()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.islower()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是小写</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.isupper()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是大写</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.istitle()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有单词都是首字母大写，像标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.isspace()) <span class="comment"># 判断所有字符都是空白字符、\t、\n、\r</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="6-字符串大小写转换"><a href="#6-字符串大小写转换" class="headerlink" title="6 字符串大小写转换"></a>6 字符串大小写转换</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.upper())          <span class="comment"># 把所有字符中的小写字母转换成大写字母</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.lower())          <span class="comment"># 把所有字符中的大写字母转换成小写字母</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.capitalize())     <span class="comment"># 把第一个字母转化为大写字母，其余小写</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(str.title())          <span class="comment"># 把每个单词的第一个字母转化为大写，其余小写 </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="7-datetime-日期库"><a href="#7-datetime-日期库" class="headerlink" title="7 datetime 日期库"></a>7 datetime 日期库</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import datetime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="8-字典变列表操作"><a href="#8-字典变列表操作" class="headerlink" title="8 字典变列表操作"></a>8 字典变列表操作</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[k <span class="keyword">for</span> k, v <span class="keyword">in</span> d.items()]  <span class="comment">#取键为列表 元素为字符</span></span><br><span class="line">[v <span class="keyword">for</span> k, v <span class="keyword">in</span> d.items()]  <span class="comment">#取值为列表</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&quot;%s=%s&quot;</span> % (k, v) <span class="keyword">for</span> k, v <span class="keyword">in</span> params.items()]  <span class="comment">#以规定形式 将键值对转换为列表</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="9-列表过滤操作"><a href="#9-列表过滤操作" class="headerlink" title="9 列表过滤操作"></a>9 列表过滤操作</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[i <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> li <span class="keyword">if</span> len(i) &gt; 1] <span class="comment">#遍历列表将串长大于1的取出作列表</span></span><br><span class="line">条件可随情况更改如 i!= <span class="string">&quot;x&quot;</span> 等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
